</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-55_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-56_ pf-text-1"><strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong> - Sets guidelines for the collection and processing of personal data within the EU.






